1
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:41,020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,090 --> 00:01:43,920
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,310
When will it open?

4
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,920
Very soon.

5
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,480
With such good news,

6
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,590
why didn't you inform me?

7
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:08,120
Mr. Duan.

8
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:08,960
Ms. Xu.

9
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,370
Mr. Xue.

10
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:11,390
Chef Li.

11
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:12,940
Mr. Ji.

12
00:02:13,090 --> 00:02:15,350
This is quite a fresh combination today.

13
00:02:18,310 --> 00:02:19,680
I've long heard that

14
00:02:20,100 --> 00:02:23,980
Chef Li has been working on
the recipe of Yan Du Xian.

15
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:26,550
Now that I've seen this dish today,

16
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:28,810
I wonder if I have the luck to taste it.

17
00:02:31,450 --> 00:02:33,170
Yes, yes, yes.

18
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:35,320
Let me do it.

19
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,360
Taste it now.

20
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:42,079
Okay.

21
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,280
Be careful. It's hot.

22
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,720
What do you think, Mr. Duan?

23
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:00,480
It's kind of interesting.

24
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:02,970
Mr. Ji.

25
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,620
When the restaurant opens,

26
00:03:04,620 --> 00:03:05,910
save a few tables for me.

27
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:08,570
I'll come support
the Chinese restaurant, too.

28
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,470
Mr. Duan,
if you visit our Chinese restaurant,

29
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:12,190
how could a few tables be enough?

30
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:14,370
All our private rooms on the third floor
will be reserved for you.

31
00:03:14,370 --> 00:03:15,030
Okay.

32
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,030
As for the people,

33
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,400
you can have as many as you want.

34
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,740
But when it comes to the reputation,

35
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:20,340
you have to earn it yourself.

36
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:23,600
Of course.

37
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,120
Mr. Duan.

38
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,050
Chef Jia is asking...

39
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:30,120
Um...

40
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:31,400
Tell him not to worry.

41
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:32,470
I won't

42
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:34,470
give the Purong Chinese Restaurant

43
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:36,329
any chance to turn things around.

44
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:39,570
When will their restaurant open?

45
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:42,550
On the 18th of this month.

46
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:48,600
Let's just make it shut down
on the opening day of their restaurant.

47
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:54,560
It's almost ready.

48
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,890
I think we can eat it now.

49
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,800
We are having a special meal here

50
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,360
without inviting Mr. Xue.

51
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,520
Will he be unhappy?

52
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:03,950
Who cares about him?

53
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:06,090
This is a gathering between us girls.

54
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:08,240
Here. Be careful. It's hot.

55
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:08,710
Okay.

56
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:09,240
It's hot.

57
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:17,579
Confess and you will be treated leniently.

58
00:04:17,579 --> 00:04:20,040
Did something happen
between you and Mr. Ji?

59
00:04:23,050 --> 00:04:24,480
Nothing happened.

60
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,260
No.

61
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,600
Why do I feel that

62
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,490
since we came back from our hometown,

63
00:04:29,490 --> 00:04:31,950
the vibe between you two
has been different?

64
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:35,130
Vibe? What vibe?

65
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,870
A guilty vibe.

66
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,560
Tell me the truth.

67
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:43,159
What is the hidden story between you two

68
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:44,690
that you can't even tell me?

69
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:48,520
This sweet potato is so delicious.

70
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:49,740
Taste it now.

71
00:04:49,770 --> 00:04:51,370
Stop changing the subject.

72
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:54,409
How about this?

73
00:04:54,409 --> 00:04:55,670
Let me ask another way.

74
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,850
Since you're such a sensitive person,

75
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,000
can't you sense that

76
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:02,130
Mr. Ji treats you differently
from how he treats others?

77
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:03,920
So what?

78
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,870
That depends on you.

79
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:07,390
What do you think of it?

80
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:11,160
I just got out of a failed marriage.

81
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,060
I can't move on so soon.

82
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:16,000
Stop limiting yourself, okay?

83
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:19,240
Nowadays, it's not unusual
to date three people in a year.

84
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,510
Let me tell you.

85
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:22,870
A romantic relationship
is just like a baked sweet potato.

86
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:24,600
You have to enjoy it while it's still hot.

87
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,720
But it also depends on
the right time and place.

88
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:29,120
For example,
if you're walking in a desert,

89
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:31,190
almost dying of heat and thirst,

90
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:32,620
and someone gives you
a baked sweet potato,

91
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:34,480
wouldn't that choke you to death?

92
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,270
It's the same for a romantic relationship.

93
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:39,000
If the timing is wrong,

94
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:42,350
even the best person
won't be the right one.

95
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,190
Then, right now,

96
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:49,130
do you still want to
start a new relationship?

97
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:09,290
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

98
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:12,270
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

99
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:16,410
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

100
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:19,370
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

101
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:23,510
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

102
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,270
♪ In the virtual world ♪

103
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:33,050
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

104
00:06:34,470 --> 00:06:36,390
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

105
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:40,250
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

106
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,350
♪ Until I met you ♪

107
00:06:44,150 --> 00:06:47,250
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

108
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:49,620
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

109
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:51,909
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

110
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,630
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

111
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,870
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

112
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:59,320
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

113
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:00,190
That night...

114
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:01,200
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

115
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,880
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

116
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:05,780
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

117
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,760
♪ Love really hurts ♪

118
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:08,540
[That night]

119
00:07:09,990 --> 00:07:14,650
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

120
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,830
Are you asleep?

121
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:25,480
♪ In the end, everything came to nothing ♪

122
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:19,570
[Are you asleep?]

123
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:30,220
[Miyu]

124
00:07:41,909 --> 00:07:43,650
[Miyu]

125
00:07:48,290 --> 00:07:48,850
Mr. Wei.

126
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,680
Mr. Duan Jr.

127
00:07:55,450 --> 00:07:56,580
Sorry to bother you.

128
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:58,070
Mr. Wei.

129
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,800
What brings you here?

130
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:02,190
The Chinese restaurant
will open tomorrow, won't it?

131
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:03,430
I'm up here to give you a heads-up.

132
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:05,240
We need to be on the same page.

133
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:10,540
I heard you booked a large private room.

134
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,130
What does that mean?

135
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,790
I don't quite understand it.

136
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,280
It's to celebrate the successful opening
of your hotel's Chinese restaurant.

137
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:19,480
What's there to be uable to understand?

138
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,870
Why are you putting in so much effort

139
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:22,240
for that Ji Feng?

140
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,310
You have everyone at your beck and call.

141
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:26,160
In the end,
he might get all the spotlight.

142
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,160
It's not worth it.

143
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,360
Mr. Wei, you're thinking too much.

144
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:32,440
[Purong Hotel]

145
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,680
I've merely helped you set up a stage.

146
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,669
As for how to perform this show tomorrow,

147
00:08:32,669 --> 00:08:35,330
it still depends on
which play you want to watch.

148
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,200
I knew it.

149
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,950
You and I have the same taste.

150
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,159
Alright then.

151
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,500
Since you have no dietary restrictions,

152
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:43,789
I'll arrange it as usual.

153
00:08:43,789 --> 00:08:46,200
Mr. Duan Jr., let's wait and see.

154
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,560
I'm leaving now.

155
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:50,580
[Purong Hotel]

156
00:08:57,790 --> 00:09:02,510
[Staff Only]

157
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:05,240
Tomorrow, the private room
in the Chinese restaurant

158
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,770
will turn into a lion's den.

159
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:09,120
I wonder what kind of shady characters

160
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,050
Duan Aoxiang will bring over here.

161
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:12,690
Mr. Ji,

162
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:15,440
should we ask more people
to keep an eye on things tomorrow?

163
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,670
I'll be on compensatory leave tomorrow.

164
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:18,400
I can come over and help Qiaoqi.

165
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,790
Alright. It's settled then.

166
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:22,910
You'll be fully
in charge of the private room tomorrow.

167
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:24,320
Let me know if anything happens.

168
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,010
Okay.

169
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,120
Let's go.

170
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,640
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

171
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,320
[Staff Only]

172
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:10,410
[Food Storage Box]

173
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:15,230
You really scared me!

174
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:17,120
What are you doing here?

175
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:19,510
I'm here to see you and the cured pork.

176
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:20,200
My foot has just healed,

177
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,660
and now you've hit my head.

178
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,540
-I'm sorry.
-Are you okay?

179
00:10:23,630 --> 00:10:25,560
What's wrong? Is the meat alright?

180
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:27,110
It's perfectly fine.

181
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:33,720
What's wrong? Is there a problem?

182
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:42,400
There's something wrong with the meat.

183
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:52,510
Don't worry.
The cured pork will be there soon.

184
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:03,960
I can't believe
there's a mole in the kitchen.

185
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,840
When I catch this despicable scumbag,

186
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,170
I'll stuff this meat right into his mouth.

187
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,300
Wait!

188
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:19,510
Since they were so kind
to give us the meat,

189
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,570
wouldn't it be a waste to throw it away?

190
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:41,020
[Welcome to Purong Chinese Restaurant]

191
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:44,840
Come on, guys.

192
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:44,720
[Purong Chinese Restaurant]

193
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,910
Today is the first day

194
00:11:46,490 --> 00:11:48,190
[Purong Chinese Restaurant]

195
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:48,270
of Purong Chinese Restaurant's reopening.

196
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:50,330
Everyone, present a brand-new image

197
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,840
to welcome all the upcoming guests.

198
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,360
Okay?

199
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,280
Okay!

200
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,530
Mr. Yang.

201
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:55,510
Mr. Ji.

202
00:11:55,710 --> 00:11:56,770
Thanks for coming.

203
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,380
Congratulations.

204
00:11:58,630 --> 00:12:01,010
Today, I'm going to
taste the food carefully.

205
00:12:01,010 --> 00:12:03,460
Yes, you have to taste it carefully today.

206
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,680
Stir-fried Eel with Eight Delicacies.

207
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,630
Eleven plates of Shanghai Smoked Fish.

208
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:09,960
Serve as many
Osmanthus Rice Cakes as we have.

209
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:10,480
Sit.

210
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:15,890
Fetch a high chair.

211
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:19,910
Ms. Xu.

212
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,750
I didn't expect Mr. Ji would send you here
to control the scene personally.

213
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:24,030
I'm flattered, Mr. Duan.

214
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:25,390
Today, we have so many guests here.

215
00:12:25,390 --> 00:12:27,420
It's my honor to serve everyone.

216
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:28,440
Come in, please.

217
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:30,880
Welcome.

218
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,510
Please.

219
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,440
The private room is already full.

220
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:37,760
There are still six empty tables
in the main hall.

221
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,360
Take care.

222
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:41,300
Not a single table can be empty today.

223
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:42,770
Ask our clerks to give the guests
in the HSKP Department

224
00:12:42,770 --> 00:12:44,230
some Chinese restaurant vouchers.

225
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:44,870
Okay.

226
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:48,990
Hello, Mr. Duan Jr.

227
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:49,870
Mr. Duan Jr.

228
00:12:49,890 --> 00:12:51,360
-You guys are here, too.
-Mr. Duan Jr.

229
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,440
Have a seat. Sit.

230
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:53,870
Where is the Crab Roe Tofu?

231
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:55,120
-Is it ready?
-Almost!

232
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,240
The people upstairs
are pushing for Yan Du Xian.

233
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,370
It'll be ready soon.

234
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:13,510
Serve it.

235
00:13:18,910 --> 00:13:19,630
Luo!

236
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,840
Come and help!

237
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,880
Why are we changing it, Qiaoqi?

238
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:30,850
We'll have a good show to watch soon.

239
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,750
Zhi.

240
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,630
How does this taste?

241
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,270
Where did you purchase

242
00:13:46,130 --> 00:13:49,020
[Purong Hotel]

243
00:13:46,270 --> 00:13:47,600
this salted meat?

244
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,550
It doesn't even taste right.

245
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:52,410
Didn't the chef taste it
before the food was served?

246
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,600
Is this what you call a signature dish?

247
00:13:56,420 --> 00:14:00,060
[Purong Hotel]

248
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,330
It's so disappointing.

249
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,320
Today, I've even

250
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:02,990
specially invited Zhi here.

251
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:04,950
In front of so many of my friends,

252
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:07,670
how can I get out of
this awkward situation?

253
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:13,310
[Purong Hotel]

254
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:09,140
Well, my dear friends,

255
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:10,720
it's my treat today.

256
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:13,510
Now let's go to Kuanli Mingjue
across the street.

257
00:14:13,510 --> 00:14:14,630
The head chef there

258
00:14:14,630 --> 00:14:16,750
has prepared
the authentic Yan Du Xian for you all.

259
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:17,890
[Purong Hotel]

260
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:18,150
Oh, by the way,

261
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:19,390
our head chef in Kuanli

262
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:22,270
is Jia Shikun, who came from here.

263
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:25,120
He's the famous Chef Jia
in the Shanghai Bund.

264
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,320
His specialty dish

265
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,410
happens to be

266
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,250
Yan Du Xian.

267
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:32,170
Mr. Duan, please wait.

268
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,240
Everyone,

269
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:36,480
please give me some time

270
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,670
to say a few words.

271
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:39,270
Please have a seat.

272
00:14:39,270 --> 00:14:40,080
Actually,

273
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:42,240
that bowl of food you just ate

274
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:44,730
wasn't our signature dish, Yan Du Xian.

275
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:47,270
It was just a small interlude.

276
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,000
As for the exact details

277
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,390
of the story behind it,

278
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:52,080
I'd like to invite you all to taste

279
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:54,870
our real signature dish,
Yan Du Xian, first.

280
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:56,130
And then I will tell you

281
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,440
the whole story.

282
00:14:59,890 --> 00:15:00,590
Come on.

283
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:01,520
Miyu.

284
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:13,310
Be careful.

285
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,400
Zhi.

286
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:18,360
I'd like to invite you
to taste the Yan Du Xian

287
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:20,120
which our head chef simmered
with the ingredients

288
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,580
she personally selected.

289
00:15:22,020 --> 00:15:22,660
Please.

290
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:34,550
This flavor...

291
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:36,200
is so fresh,

292
00:15:36,550 --> 00:15:37,270
so wild

293
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:38,330
and so strong.

294
00:15:38,330 --> 00:15:39,210
I like it.

295
00:15:40,110 --> 00:15:41,120
So previously...

296
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:44,790
Previously, a distinguished guest

297
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:47,050
heard that we would host a dinner
for VIPs today,

298
00:15:47,050 --> 00:15:50,230
so he specially brought us
a piece of salted meat last night.

299
00:15:50,230 --> 00:15:52,270
Then our general manager felt

300
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:54,340
it would be ungracious
to refuse such kindness,

301
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:55,670
so he asked us to use

302
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:57,600
the best broth and the best ingredients

303
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:59,270
to simmer this salted meat.

304
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,910
Perhaps our capabilities are so limited

305
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:03,480
that we really couldn't
handle such a precious gift.

306
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:06,030
That's the cause
of what happened just now.

307
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:07,030
I'm sorry

308
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,550
to let you see this awkward situation.

309
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:10,410
Who is this distinguished guest?

310
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:13,030
It doesn't matter

311
00:16:13,030 --> 00:16:14,510
who this distinguished guest is.

312
00:16:14,510 --> 00:16:15,630
What's important is that

313
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:16,280
Mr. Duan

314
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:18,670
has invited you here today.

315
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:21,080
Your sharp comment just now

316
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,390
really gave us

317
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:24,240
enough confidence and recognition.

318
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,670
We are extremely grateful.

319
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:28,550
It looks like this young lady
is really good at telling stories.

320
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:29,840
I'm going to include this information

321
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:31,120
in my review.

322
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:35,510
Being able to read our hotel's own story

323
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:37,770
in your food review column

324
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:40,000
would be our greatest honor.

325
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,390
Zhi, I'd also like to thank you

326
00:16:41,390 --> 00:16:43,790
for strongly recommending
our hotel's signature dish,

327
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:45,510
Yan Du Xian.

328
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,930
It looks like this Purong Hotel

329
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:55,630
is still as good as ever.

330
00:16:58,510 --> 00:17:00,290
It's a time-honored brand after all.

331
00:17:00,290 --> 00:17:02,150
It really deserves its reputation.

332
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:02,910
Let's eat.

333
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:04,109
Let's all eat.

334
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:26,040
Thanks. Enjoy your meal.

335
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,920
Are you satisfied with the dishes?

336
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,780
-They're good.
-Enjoy your meal.

337
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:36,590
Ma'am,

338
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,180
are you satisfied with the dishes today?

339
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:43,400
They're great. I'm very satisfied.

340
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:46,650
I won't disturb you then.
Please enjoy your meal.

341
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:01,900
Chef Jia is asking

342
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,510
when the guests will arrive.

343
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:04,840
Why are you even asking?

344
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:06,130
Can't you sense it?

345
00:18:06,330 --> 00:18:07,330
I got it, Mr. Duan.

346
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:10,950
Come on, Mr. Duan Jr.

347
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:12,880
Come on, Zhi.

348
00:18:12,990 --> 00:18:14,090
The food is good.

349
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:15,340
Of course.

350
00:18:15,370 --> 00:18:16,810
Enjoy your meal.

351
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:22,590
Mr. Wang.

352
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:23,900
Thanks for coming.

353
00:18:23,900 --> 00:18:25,270
Let me know if you need anything.

354
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:26,240
Thank you.

355
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,170
Enjoy your meal.

356
00:18:31,630 --> 00:18:32,880
Everyone is eating, huh?

357
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:33,960
Welcome.

358
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:35,760
Zhi.

359
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:36,780
How does it taste?

360
00:18:38,430 --> 00:18:42,710
The flavors of the four seasons
are all in these dishes.

361
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,020
Is that so?

362
00:18:45,330 --> 00:18:46,090
Mr. Duan Jr.,

363
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:48,370
it looks like you're all very satisfied.

364
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:50,380
We're very satisfied. It's very good.

365
00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:51,510
It's really so good.

366
00:18:51,530 --> 00:18:53,330
Why don't you taste it yourself?

367
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:57,580
Let me taste it.

368
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:03,680
The flavor is indeed extraordinary.

369
00:19:07,510 --> 00:19:08,350
Enjoy your meal.

370
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:09,110
Excuse me.

371
00:19:16,130 --> 00:19:16,930
Mr. Duan Jr.!

372
00:19:17,790 --> 00:19:18,590
Mr. Duan Jr.!

373
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:20,110
Well...

374
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,590
I thought you would understand

375
00:19:22,590 --> 00:19:23,750
my good intentions

376
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:24,960
and help me.

377
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:28,510
I didn't expect you to come here
and see how embarrassed I was.

378
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:30,430
Mr. Duan Jr., you've misunderstood.

379
00:19:30,430 --> 00:19:31,920
I was also kept in the dark.

380
00:19:32,790 --> 00:19:34,070
I made arrangements.

381
00:19:34,090 --> 00:19:36,240
Who would have thought
it would turn out like this?

382
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,090
Alright.

383
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:39,670
Anyway, I've shown enough respect for you.

384
00:19:39,670 --> 00:19:41,130
And I've invited the VIPs.

385
00:19:41,530 --> 00:19:43,730
Then you'll have to pay for this meal.

386
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:47,150
Mr. Duan Jr.!

387
00:19:50,410 --> 00:19:52,880
Let's drink to the successful opening
of the Chinese restaurant!

388
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,550
Cheers!

389
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:02,880
It's all thanks to your efforts today.

390
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:05,400
Otherwise,
I would have ruined our reputation.

391
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,880
Speaking of that guy, Guo Luda,

392
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,610
I definitely won't let him off.

393
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:11,310
As a dignified senior chef skilled in
both hot dishes and pastry making,

394
00:20:11,310 --> 00:20:13,310
how could he play dirty tricks on me
behind my back?

395
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:14,440
It's a reasonable suspicion,

396
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,510
but we have no solid evidence,

397
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:17,640
so we still can't jump to conclusions.

398
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:20,000
Everyone knows about the opening
of the Chinese restaurant.

399
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,200
If someone is really hiding in the corner

400
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,480
to cause trouble for us,

401
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:25,410
it'll be hard to guard against him.

402
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,590
So, Qiaoqi,

403
00:20:27,590 --> 00:20:30,440
I hope from now on, you can
think twice before taking action.

404
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,640
Impulse is the devil.

405
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:34,460
The kitchen isn't a place
just anyone can enter.

406
00:20:34,460 --> 00:20:35,220
Qiaoqi.

407
00:20:36,090 --> 00:20:39,250
You're the head chef
of the Chinese restaurant now.

408
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:42,440
You have a clear view
of everything in the kitchen.

409
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:45,510
No one has a broader perspective than you.

410
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,070
At this time, if you slowly

411
00:20:47,070 --> 00:20:49,200
calm down and observe everyone,

412
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:52,090
bad guys are all afraid of being exposed.

413
00:20:52,090 --> 00:20:54,220
The fox will definitely show its tail.

414
00:20:54,870 --> 00:20:56,240
Now that I've heard what you said,

415
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:58,200
the swapping of the cured pork

416
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:01,440
must have something to do
with Duan Aoxiang.

417
00:21:01,460 --> 00:21:02,860
I have that feeling, too.

418
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:04,490
In the private room today,

419
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:06,510
Mr. Duan almost took everyone on the spot

420
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:08,030
straight to Kuanli.

421
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:09,030
It was as if they had been

422
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:10,550
prepared for it all along.

423
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,830
That's consistent with the news
I've gathered.

424
00:21:13,830 --> 00:21:16,430
I've heard
in terms of Duan Aoxiang's banquet,

425
00:21:16,510 --> 00:21:19,110
Kuanli was also preparing for it
at the same time.

426
00:21:19,110 --> 00:21:21,110
I guess if we had made ourselves
laughingstocks here,

427
00:21:21,110 --> 00:21:23,480
they could just take everyone
straight to Kuanli.

428
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:25,880
So fortunately,
we found out about it in time.

429
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:27,830
Chef Jia sharpened his knife in vain.

430
00:21:27,830 --> 00:21:30,150
It's getting clearer
who caused this trouble.

431
00:21:30,150 --> 00:21:32,500
Duan Aoxiang, that wretched playboy.

432
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:33,980
Speaking of which,

433
00:21:34,110 --> 00:21:34,680
today,

434
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:37,310
although it looked like a good start,

435
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,030
in fact, most of the guests

436
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:40,920
were well-connected people
or relatives and friends.

437
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:42,110
As for the rest, we just relied on

438
00:21:42,110 --> 00:21:44,150
discount coupons to create a buzz.

439
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:45,880
There were still not many new guests.

440
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:47,510
I don't know how things will be tomorrow.

441
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:50,840
I've already asked the sales department
to print vouchers.

442
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,310
Tell them to prepare more.

443
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:54,720
If the situation is still not good
tomorrow morning,

444
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:58,050
ask the HSKP Department
to give more vouchers to the guests.

445
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:58,950
In short,

446
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:01,270
the first three days after the opening
are just like a movie's

447
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:02,750
opening weekend box office.

448
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:04,510
Success or failure is crucial.

449
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:07,280
Cheers.

450
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:11,140
Looking forward to tomorrow.

451
00:22:17,090 --> 00:22:18,190
I'm starving.

452
00:22:18,510 --> 00:22:20,310
Why hasn't the food arrived yet?

453
00:22:35,030 --> 00:22:36,430
What's for dinner today?

454
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:40,570
White Gourd Soup with Cured Pork and Kelp,

455
00:22:41,030 --> 00:22:42,690
Braised Rice with Cured Pork,

456
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:45,720
Cured Pork with Tofu

457
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:48,500
and Cured Pork with Agrocybe Mushrooms.

458
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:50,830
Alright. All the dishes are served.

459
00:22:50,830 --> 00:22:51,800
Please enjoy your meal.

460
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:52,350
Wait.

461
00:22:55,670 --> 00:22:56,260
What...

462
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:57,680
does this mean?

463
00:22:59,070 --> 00:23:01,640
Thank you for inviting
a table full of gourmets today

464
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:03,380
to support our Chinese restaurant.

465
00:23:03,380 --> 00:23:05,980
This is a luxury dinner
specially made for you.

466
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:08,510
What's this smell?

467
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,110
Are you trying to poison me?

468
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:11,270
Of course not.

469
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:13,510
This all-cured-pork feast

470
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:15,240
was prepared with the cured pork
our mysterious VIP

471
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:17,030
had sent to our kitchen.

472
00:23:17,270 --> 00:23:19,270
These are top-notch ingredients.

473
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:21,110
How would anyone else deserve to eat them?

474
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:24,770
From now on, it'll be a special offer
for this presidential suite.

475
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:27,610
I won't disturb you then.
Please enjoy your meal.

476
00:23:28,550 --> 00:23:29,150
By the way,

477
00:23:29,770 --> 00:23:31,030
it's more than enough.

478
00:23:34,120 --> 00:23:35,480
Just wait, you all!

479
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:53,720
There are so many people.

480
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:55,030
Are they all waiting for tables?

481
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:56,020
Yes, they are.

482
00:23:56,050 --> 00:23:57,050
Li! Li!

483
00:23:57,770 --> 00:23:59,980
Tell the kitchen to hurry up
and get ready.

484
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:00,790
Okay.

485
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:06,110
Come on!

486
00:24:06,290 --> 00:24:07,540
The soup is ready!

487
00:24:27,380 --> 00:24:28,680
Can the Yan Du Xian be served now?

488
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:29,310
Yes, it can.

489
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:30,680
Okay. Let's go.

490
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:32,030
Waiter!

491
00:24:32,030 --> 00:24:33,480
I've been calling for a long time.
Where's the waiter?

492
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:34,440
Coming soon.

493
00:24:35,250 --> 00:24:37,450
Waiter, we want to order more food here!

494
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:41,330
What a good meal!

495
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:42,230
Let's go.

496
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:43,640
Is there anyone else who wants to order?

497
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:44,920
I want a portion of Yan Du Xian.

498
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:46,350
To order more food,
please click on this first.

499
00:24:46,350 --> 00:24:47,030
Come here!

500
00:24:47,030 --> 00:24:48,430
Serve this table! Hurry!

501
00:24:48,590 --> 00:24:50,150
Waiter, I want more drinks.

502
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,110
We still have one dish
that hasn't been served yet.

503
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:51,790
Hurry up.

504
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,030
Coming soon.

505
00:24:58,090 --> 00:24:59,230
Go help them now.

506
00:25:03,490 --> 00:25:05,550
Waiter, is our food ready?

507
00:25:05,550 --> 00:25:06,510
Coming soon.

508
00:25:08,270 --> 00:25:09,270
How does it taste?

509
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:10,260
It's quite good.

510
00:25:10,280 --> 00:25:11,220
Enjoy your meal.

511
00:25:17,530 --> 00:25:18,770
When will the Eight-Treasure Duck
be ready?

512
00:25:18,770 --> 00:25:20,510
If the Braised Fish Tail
still isn't ready, the guest will leave.

513
00:25:20,510 --> 00:25:21,310
Coming!

514
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:23,470
How is it today?

515
00:25:23,490 --> 00:25:24,600
Is the business outside very good?

516
00:25:24,600 --> 00:25:25,730
It's more than good.

517
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:27,620
It's booming. A roaring success.

518
00:25:28,730 --> 00:25:29,740
Everyone!

519
00:25:30,090 --> 00:25:31,600
Did you hear that?

520
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,260
The business is booming today.

521
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:35,520
Let's all hurry up.

522
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:37,100
The guests like our food.

523
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:39,110
Whatever skills you have,

524
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:40,240
show them all.

525
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:41,240
Did you hear that?

526
00:25:41,260 --> 00:25:42,620
Yes!

527
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:47,750
At this time, if you slowly

528
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:49,760
calm down and observe everyone,

529
00:25:49,780 --> 00:25:51,480
bad guys are all afraid of being exposed.

530
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:53,610
The fox will definitely show its tail.

531
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:56,800
I'll emphasize this again.

532
00:25:56,930 --> 00:25:59,310
Today's Yan Du Xian is the top priority

533
00:25:59,340 --> 00:26:00,880
and plays the absolute key role.

534
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:03,190
The clay pots are stewing on the stoves.

535
00:26:03,210 --> 00:26:05,670
The cured pork is frozen
in the storage room.

536
00:26:05,940 --> 00:26:08,090
Those who have sticky fingers
should stay away.

537
00:26:08,090 --> 00:26:09,750
If anyone dares to
cause trouble for me again,

538
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:11,080
I'll teach him a lesson.

539
00:26:13,110 --> 00:26:14,310
Well, what do you mean?

540
00:26:14,310 --> 00:26:15,590
Who are you talking about?

541
00:26:15,590 --> 00:26:17,420
Li Qiaoqi, make it clear.

542
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:18,840
Stop being sarcastic here.

543
00:26:18,840 --> 00:26:19,720
Mr. Guo.

544
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:21,360
Why are you overreacting?

545
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:23,040
Have I stepped on your tail?

546
00:26:24,270 --> 00:26:25,310
If I, Guo Luda,

547
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:26,830
had ever touched your cured pork,

548
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:29,030
I-I-I'd change my surname to yours, Li.

549
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,400
Why are you always making

550
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,830
sarcastic comments in this kitchen?

551
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:32,960
When can you stop?

552
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:33,880
If you don't like me,

553
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,000
you can just fire me.

554
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:37,270
If you want to
domineer over me and bully me,

555
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,790
believe it or not,
I would perform a suplex on you.

556
00:26:38,790 --> 00:26:39,510
Come on!

557
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:40,510
I'll do it now!

558
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:41,930
I'll just do it!

559
00:26:42,100 --> 00:26:43,310
Guys!

560
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,750
Calm down!

561
00:26:44,770 --> 00:26:45,830
The guests outside in the restaurant
are pushing for their food.

562
00:26:45,830 --> 00:26:47,830
They're about to tear the roof down.

563
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:49,480
You can fight another day.

564
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:49,920
Okay?

565
00:26:50,130 --> 00:26:50,880
Heroine.

566
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,070
Good guy.

567
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:56,740
You only know how to smooth things over
and talk like a bureaucrat.

568
00:26:57,330 --> 00:26:58,230
Calm down.

569
00:26:59,510 --> 00:27:01,460
Qiaoqi. Qiaoqi.

570
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:03,170
Don't always be so emotional.

571
00:27:05,390 --> 00:27:07,420
I'm the one who's being unprofessional.

572
00:27:07,420 --> 00:27:08,700
Mr. Xue, I'm very busy.

573
00:27:08,730 --> 00:27:09,530
Excuse me.

574
00:27:12,890 --> 00:27:14,220
Everyone, work harder!

575
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:15,510
Okay!

576
00:27:26,050 --> 00:27:27,920
Hello, how many tables are there
before my turn?

577
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:29,270
There are five or six tables
before your turn.

578
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:30,680
Please wait a bit longer.

579
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,750
There are still five or six tables?

580
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:33,410
Yes, please wait a bit longer.

581
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:35,110
This way.

582
00:27:36,070 --> 00:27:38,200
This is the guest from Room 1815.

583
00:27:38,300 --> 00:27:39,370
Hello.

584
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:41,960
Are you still planning to check out today?

585
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:42,550
Yes.

586
00:27:42,990 --> 00:27:45,720
Isn't it fine
as long as I check out before 2:00 PM?

587
00:27:45,830 --> 00:27:46,550
2:00 PM

588
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:48,500
is our deadline for late checkout.

589
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:51,450
If there were no guests,
we could definitely make exceptions.

590
00:27:51,450 --> 00:27:54,300
But right now,
there are indeed guests waiting.

591
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:55,880
It's not that I don't want to check out.

592
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:56,750
The key is that

593
00:27:56,750 --> 00:27:59,270
I just don't know
when my number will be called,

594
00:27:59,270 --> 00:28:00,200
so I don't dare to leave

595
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:01,800
and go back to pack my things.

596
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:03,800
Do you think this is okay?

597
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:05,290
I'll wait in line for you here.

598
00:28:05,290 --> 00:28:06,700
You can go back to pack your things first.

599
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:08,700
Come down after you've checked out.

600
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,640
Alright. Thank you.

601
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:11,280
You're welcome.

602
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:13,140
Then please come this way with me.

603
00:28:13,870 --> 00:28:14,790
Sorry for the trouble, Ms. Xu.

604
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:15,590
It's my duty.

605
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,880
This way, please.

606
00:28:22,410 --> 00:28:25,110
Luo Qingping, I'm handling something
at the Chinese restaurant.

607
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:27,440
If anything happens upstairs,
let me know anytime.

608
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:28,240
Roger that.

609
00:28:30,490 --> 00:28:31,620
Mr. Ji.

610
00:28:31,650 --> 00:28:33,540
Gao from the Purchasing Department

611
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:35,260
is both inarticulate and bad-tempered.

612
00:28:35,260 --> 00:28:37,510
That's the reason why he loses out.

613
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:39,650
Having worked on hotel finance
for so many years,

614
00:28:39,650 --> 00:28:41,240
he still doesn't understand
worldly wisdom.

615
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:42,100
[Huang Chengmin]

616
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:43,350
But he's a really good person

617
00:28:43,190 --> 00:28:45,690
[Xue Rui]

618
00:28:43,350 --> 00:28:45,510
and is absolutely loyal to our hotel.

619
00:28:45,510 --> 00:28:46,640
Mr. Ji, you can't just listen to

620
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:48,750
the one-sided story of the whistleblowers.

621
00:28:47,460 --> 00:28:49,020
[Where are you?]

622
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:52,240
Mr. Huang.

623
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:54,350
We've already handed this matter over

624
00:28:54,350 --> 00:28:56,610
to the Business Management Department.

625
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,520
I know you quite cherish talented people.

626
00:28:58,520 --> 00:28:59,470
I understand.

627
00:28:59,490 --> 00:29:01,810
But let's wait
for the investigation results.

628
00:29:01,810 --> 00:29:02,520
Okay?

629
00:29:13,950 --> 00:29:15,960
You can look at the menu
and order your food first.

630
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,830
It will be quicker when you go in later.

631
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:18,760
Okay. Thank you.

632
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:23,070
You can bring two more tables
of guests up here.

633
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:23,550
Okay.

634
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:25,550
Guests over here, please follow me.

635
00:29:25,670 --> 00:29:27,280
This way, please.

636
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,370
Are you okay?

637
00:29:49,810 --> 00:29:50,720
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

638
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:51,320
I'm sorry.

639
00:29:51,550 --> 00:29:52,170
It's fine.

640
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:53,110
Clean it up.

641
00:30:09,690 --> 00:30:10,930
Let me wipe it for you.

642
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:15,350
Is it hot?

643
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:16,470
It's fine.

644
00:30:26,670 --> 00:30:27,710
It's not very hot.

645
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:34,580
By the way,

646
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:36,560
why are there so many people
at the entrance?

647
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:38,220
Did something happen inside?

648
00:30:39,590 --> 00:30:42,310
Nothing happened.
Business is just really good today.

649
00:30:42,310 --> 00:30:44,290
The guests are all lining up for tables.

650
00:30:44,290 --> 00:30:45,500
But don't worry.

651
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:47,180
Mr. Xue is inside,

652
00:30:47,270 --> 00:30:48,720
and Qiaoqi is in the kitchen.

653
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,750
Everything is arranged.

654
00:30:49,750 --> 00:30:51,730
It's just that the guests keep coming
one after another.

655
00:30:51,730 --> 00:30:52,590
How about this?

656
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:53,830
Let's open up the coffee bar

657
00:30:53,830 --> 00:30:55,480
to the waiting guests as well.

658
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,200
Good idea. I'll go right now.

659
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:57,750
Okay.

660
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,200
How is it going, guys?

661
00:31:18,590 --> 00:31:20,350
Can your wrists still handle it?

662
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:21,310
Your wrists!

663
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,920
Tell the guests outside

664
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,640
there's not much Yan Du Xian left.

665
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:26,830
How much is left exactly?

666
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:27,640
Ya!

667
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:36,510
Ten portions at most.

668
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:38,950
Ten portions aren't enough, Ma'am.

669
00:31:39,110 --> 00:31:40,790
There are at least 50 tables outside.

670
00:31:40,790 --> 00:31:41,790
50 tables!

671
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:43,920
That's why I'm asking you
to go out and inform them now.

672
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:45,440
Tell them to come back tomorrow
if they want it.

673
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,640
They've been waiting for over an hour.

674
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:47,640
If I tell them to come back tomorrow,

675
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,680
wouldn't I get beaten up?

676
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:50,240
There's only one piece of meat left.

677
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:52,160
Once it's eaten up, it'd be useless
even if you cut off my flesh.

678
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,440
Do as I said
and just go out to tell them.

679
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:54,160
The earlier you tell them,

680
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,020
the lighter the beating would be.

681
00:32:01,810 --> 00:32:02,940
My crabs.

682
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:04,800
They're overcooked.

683
00:32:20,110 --> 00:32:21,610
Are you two satisfied with our dishes?

684
00:32:21,610 --> 00:32:22,400
Not bad.

685
00:32:22,420 --> 00:32:23,240
Please enjoy your meal.

686
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:24,040
Okay.

687
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,310
Are you two satisfied with our dishes?

688
00:32:32,310 --> 00:32:33,350
They're good.

689
00:32:33,350 --> 00:32:34,880
Thank you. Enjoy your meal.

690
00:32:41,010 --> 00:32:42,490
You've seen the good news.

691
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,480
Do you want to hear the bad news?

692
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,010
Go ahead.

693
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:47,170
We're running out of the cured pork.

694
00:32:47,170 --> 00:32:48,470
I called the Chunlai couple.

695
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:50,280
They promised
to deliver the meat right away.

696
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:52,390
You're just amazing.

697
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,720
Everyone here can testify that

698
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,030
both of our families
arrived at the same time

699
00:32:56,030 --> 00:32:57,180
and took numbers at the same time.

700
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:59,310
It was just a matter
of who stretched out his hand first.

701
00:32:59,310 --> 00:33:01,550
Just now, we let you go first
when getting the numbers,

702
00:33:01,550 --> 00:33:02,640
but now you're trying to

703
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,000
snatch food from our mouths.

704
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,640
Just for a portion of Yan Du Xian,

705
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:06,790
aren't you ashamed to do this?

706
00:33:06,790 --> 00:33:08,240
Then what do you mean?

707
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,480
Are you not ashamed?

708
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:11,880
Our number is clearly ahead of yours,

709
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:14,030
but now you're forcing us to yield to you.

710
00:33:14,030 --> 00:33:15,500
Why should we agree?

711
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:16,230
Then tell me

712
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:16,960
what you mean.

713
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:17,790
Stop arguing.

714
00:33:17,790 --> 00:33:18,480
Don't scare the children.

715
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:19,960
Neither of the families is wrong.

716
00:33:19,960 --> 00:33:21,310
Failing to let everyone eat Yan Du Xian

717
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:22,790
is the responsibility
of our Chinese restaurant.

718
00:33:22,790 --> 00:33:24,480
But there's really
nothing we can do today.

719
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,830
-I'm really sorry.
-Um, wait.

720
00:33:25,830 --> 00:33:26,310
We...

721
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:27,270
What about us?

722
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,740
We've waited for so long.

723
00:33:28,740 --> 00:33:31,270
You advertised this Yan Du Xian
from the beginning.

724
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,550
Now we're here,

725
00:33:32,550 --> 00:33:34,480
but you're telling us it's sold out.

726
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:36,000
Isn't that a scam?

727
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:36,720
I'm sorry.

728
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,850
The key is that we...

729
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:40,040
I have an idea.

730
00:33:41,030 --> 00:33:42,360
I'm so sorry, everyone.

731
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:44,200
For the sake of the kids,

732
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:46,130
please calm down.

733
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,310
I have an idea.

734
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:49,480
Let's see if both of your families

735
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:51,130
could share one portion of Yan Du Xian.

736
00:33:51,130 --> 00:33:53,750
We can divide the large clay pot
into single-serving small bowls.

737
00:33:53,750 --> 00:33:55,480
In this way, both families can eat it.

738
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:57,160
What's more, the single-serving bowls

739
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:58,750
will be a bit cheaper.

740
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:00,350
Additionally,

741
00:34:00,350 --> 00:34:02,790
we can also give you

742
00:34:02,790 --> 00:34:04,880
two free desserts for the two kids.

743
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:06,680
In this way,
everyone can get to eat and drink,

744
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:08,150
and the kids can even play together.

745
00:34:08,150 --> 00:34:09,150
Do you think that's okay?

746
00:34:09,150 --> 00:34:10,030
-Okay!
-Okay!

747
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:11,690
That sounds great.

748
00:34:11,810 --> 00:34:13,429
Sir, please inform the kitchen.

749
00:34:13,429 --> 00:34:15,360
I'm going to kitchen to take a look.

750
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:17,070
T-Then what about us?

751
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:17,920
What about us?

752
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,230
We want to eat Yan Du Xian, too.

753
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:20,110
I'm sorry.

754
00:34:20,110 --> 00:34:22,230
The situation today is really so special.

755
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:24,230
I apologize to you all here first.

756
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:27,760
Professor Liu?

757
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:30,150
The two of us usually
can't eat up a whole portion anyway.

758
00:34:30,150 --> 00:34:31,710
If anyone agrees,

759
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:34,710
we don't mind
sharing a portion of Yan Du Xian with him.

760
00:34:34,810 --> 00:34:36,690
We can change to small portions, too.

761
00:34:36,690 --> 00:34:37,949
Thank you, Professor Liu.

762
00:34:37,949 --> 00:34:38,989
Thank you all.

763
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,710
How about this, everyone?

764
00:34:41,710 --> 00:34:43,360
Then I'll ask this lady

765
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:44,710
to count up how many people

766
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:46,070
are willing to share Yan Du Xian.

767
00:34:46,070 --> 00:34:47,880
Then I'll go back to the restaurant

768
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:49,630
and ask the guests
whose dishes haven't been served yet

769
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:50,630
to see if anyone wants to spare

770
00:34:50,630 --> 00:34:52,190
more servings to share with you.

771
00:34:52,190 --> 00:34:53,590
Do you think that's okay?

772
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:55,949
I think it's okay.
The manager really has a way.

773
00:34:55,949 --> 00:34:57,810
Wait a moment. I'll be right back.

774
00:34:57,990 --> 00:34:59,190
Mr. Xue! Mr. Xue!

775
00:35:00,220 --> 00:35:01,760
The delivery truck is already on its way.

776
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,440
It will arrive at the hotel at 3 PM.

777
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:05,170
Just wait to receive the goods.

778
00:35:07,950 --> 00:35:09,080
Then what about now?

779
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,630
There are less than 10 portions
of Yan Du Xian left.

780
00:35:10,630 --> 00:35:12,760
A bunch of guests are waiting outside.

781
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:18,390
Give them more discounts.

782
00:35:18,420 --> 00:35:20,330
Keep the guests no matter what.

783
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:21,800
Besides Yan Du Xian,

784
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:23,860
we have many other excellent dishes.

785
00:35:24,230 --> 00:35:25,820
Only when the guests sit down

786
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:27,680
will they know our capabilities.

787
00:35:27,940 --> 00:35:28,720
Ms. Xu.

788
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,000
How's it going outside?

789
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:31,710
I've already discussed it with the guests.

790
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:33,760
They're all willing to
exchange large pots for small bowls

791
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:35,590
and share Yan Du Xian with others.

792
00:35:35,590 --> 00:35:37,320
I'm here to ask
how many tables in the restaurant

793
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:39,320
haven't been served Yan Du Xian yet.

794
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:42,310
If three more tables are willing to share,

795
00:35:42,310 --> 00:35:44,420
all the guests outside
will be able to eat Yan Du Xian.

796
00:35:44,420 --> 00:35:45,420
That's great.

797
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:47,480
Go out and help the kitchen
communicate with the guests.

798
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,680
I'll do it right away.

799
00:35:48,710 --> 00:35:51,630
You can help me
discuss with the management department

800
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:52,760
the pricing
for a small portion of Yan Du Xian.

801
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,370
Okay.

802
00:35:58,210 --> 00:36:00,010
Thanks for your hard work, Miyu.

803
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:03,680
What's wrong?

804
00:36:05,890 --> 00:36:06,600
Nothing.

805
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,000
Yummy!

806
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:22,180
So fresh!

807
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:23,960
Really delicious!

808
00:36:24,030 --> 00:36:24,670
Very good!

809
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:25,320
Yummy!

810
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:32,840
So good.

811
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:33,480
Delicious.

812
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:34,540
Really delicious.

813
00:36:45,150 --> 00:36:46,210
This feels so good!

814
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:48,800
I haven't worked this hard in years.

815
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:49,510
Really.

816
00:36:57,370 --> 00:36:58,320
Delicious.

817
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:00,660
Once again, Qiaoqi's cooking has impro-

818
00:37:02,990 --> 00:37:04,280
When the Chinese restaurant was closed,

819
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:06,230
I really wanted to die.

820
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:09,150
I didn't expect the business would be
so good once it opened

821
00:37:09,150 --> 00:37:10,800
and everything would go so smoothly.

822
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:12,000
Mr. Ji, you've helped me

823
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,400
solve the cured pork problem twice.

824
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:16,000
You're truly the cured pork superman
of our hotel.

825
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:16,510
No, no, no.

826
00:37:16,510 --> 00:37:17,430
Don't call me that.

827
00:37:17,430 --> 00:37:18,360
It sounds weird.

828
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:22,800
Speaking of cured pork,
I haven't asked you guys yet.

829
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,550
When we went to Linglong Town previously,

830
00:37:24,550 --> 00:37:26,160
after Qiaoqi and I left,

831
00:37:26,230 --> 00:37:27,280
how did you two

832
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:28,440
spend that night on the island?

833
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:30,630
It seemed to rain quite heavily that day.

834
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:31,960
Did the ferry even stop?

835
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,710
Why are you so gossipy?

836
00:37:37,710 --> 00:37:39,150
Just eat your meat.

837
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:41,770
I'm curious.

838
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:44,780
By the way, speaking of which,

839
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:46,440
the extent to which our restaurant
was full up today

840
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,770
was indeed surprising.

841
00:37:47,890 --> 00:37:49,290
At first, I was worried

842
00:37:49,310 --> 00:37:51,870
whether someone
was trying to cause trouble

843
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:54,030
and complain about
the dishes or something.

844
00:37:54,030 --> 00:37:56,280
But later, it didn't seem to be the case.

845
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:59,630
As you said, good wine needs no bush.

846
00:38:00,030 --> 00:38:01,510
But don't you think this happened

847
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:03,170
too quickly and too suddenly?

848
00:38:03,720 --> 00:38:04,990
I know why.

849
00:38:07,590 --> 00:38:09,050
During the daytime today,

850
00:38:09,110 --> 00:38:10,440
I heard many guests

851
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:12,040
mentioning someone's name.

852
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:13,840
I guess it must be because of her.

853
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:14,710
-Who?
-Who?

854
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:17,030
Dianjiangchun.

855
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:18,590
Who is Dianjiangchun?

856
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:19,920
You don't even know her?

857
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:24,230
She's
a travel and restaurant-exploring blogger,

858
00:38:24,230 --> 00:38:25,880
who has been very active in recent years.

859
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:27,190
For any restaurant she visits,

860
00:38:27,190 --> 00:38:28,710
if she gives it a good review,

861
00:38:28,710 --> 00:38:30,440
its popularity will soar.

862
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:33,230
Dianjiangchun
really visited our Chinese restaurant.

863
00:38:33,230 --> 00:38:34,230
See? I told you so.

864
00:38:34,590 --> 00:38:36,150
I-Is this the blogger

865
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:37,230
you liked so much before?

866
00:38:37,230 --> 00:38:38,400
Yes, it's her.

867
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:41,140
She has 23,780,000 followers.

868
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:42,880
Forget it. Don't look.

869
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:43,760
You only have over 100 followers.

870
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:44,790
Don't let it get on your nerves.

871
00:38:44,790 --> 00:38:45,850
Look what she said.

872
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:49,920
The fragrance of spring
that cannot be missed

873
00:38:50,110 --> 00:38:53,610
is all in the Yan Du Xian of Purong Hotel.

874
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:55,400
Such a review

875
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:57,710
has saved us so much on advertising costs.

876
00:38:57,710 --> 00:38:58,320
Look.

877
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:01,030
We've really met our lucky star.

878
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:03,130
[Dianjiangchun]

879
00:39:05,390 --> 00:39:06,510
[Dianjiangchun]

880
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:08,080
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

881
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:09,580
Cheers!

882
00:39:09,710 --> 00:39:10,680
Cheers!

883
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:12,930
Let's drink a toast.

884
00:39:13,050 --> 00:39:13,740
Cheers.

885
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:27,230
Let me treat you to skewers
somewhere else.

886
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:29,410
We've just eaten.
Why should we have skewers?

887
00:39:29,410 --> 00:39:32,270
-Xu Miyu.
-Skewers taste differently from dinner.

888
00:39:38,270 --> 00:39:39,190
Do you have time?
